text: Henk Hemsing (20 September 1891 - 1 April 1971) was a Dutch diver. He competed in three events at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Dutch male divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
